text: Laure Gély (born 5 February 1979) is a French former gymnast. She competed in four events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint-Étienne
